{"entity":{"id":"recLKdKz1PjbJNN3h","type":"chapter","slug":"recLKdKz1PjbJNN3h","label":"Jas.1","rawId":"recLKdKz1PjbJNN3h","book":{"id":"recDk5A8p9VHMaXAC","type":"book","slug":"jas","label":"James","subtitle":"General Epistles","count":108,"description":"5 chapters, 29 people, 0 places"}},"stats":{"verses":27,"people":3,"places":0,"events":0},"nodes":[{"id":"recLKdKz1PjbJNN3h","type":"chapter","group":"focus","label":"Jas.1","slug":"jas_1","score":27},{"id":"recDk5A8p9VHMaXAC","type":"book","group":"book","label":"James","slug":"jas","score":108},{"id":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","type":"person","group":"mentioned","label":"God","slug":"god_1324","score":6},{"id":"recgkFqZovgbr3pAi","type":"person","group":"mentioned","label":"Jesus Christ","slug":"jesus_905","score":3},{"id":"recRuqBdtrgeag4gT","type":"person","group":"mentioned","label":"James (Brother of Jesus)","slug":"james_719","score":1}],"links":[{"source":"recLKdKz1PjbJNN3h","target":"recDk5A8p9VHMaXAC","label":"part of"},{"source":"recLKdKz1PjbJNN3h","target":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recLKdKz1PjbJNN3h","target":"recgkFqZovgbr3pAi","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recLKdKz1PjbJNN3h","target":"recRuqBdtrgeag4gT","label":"mentions"}],"verses":[{"id":"recMb3LQsSCZXUtuq","ref":"Jas.1.1","text":"James, a servant of God and of the Lord Jesus Christ, to the twelve tribes which are scattered abroad, greeting.","year":60},{"id":"rec2cauuO0PqSpVso","ref":"Jas.1.2","text":"My brethren, count it all joy when ye fall into divers temptations;","year":60},{"id":"recDPb7AbXMpBtaFk","ref":"Jas.1.3","text":"Knowing this, that the trying of your faith worketh patience.","year":60},{"id":"recsRLlH2qEpHdCDt","ref":"Jas.1.4","text":"But let patience have her perfect work, that ye may be perfect and entire, wanting nothing.","year":60},{"id":"recD3276Uhc1WXWLr","ref":"Jas.1.5","text":"If any of you lack wisdom, let him ask of God, that giveth to all men liberally, and upbraideth not; and it shall be given him.","year":60},{"id":"recl8MvMwJI0f2ZdQ","ref":"Jas.1.6","text":"But let him ask in faith, nothing wavering. For he that wavereth is like a wave of the sea driven with the wind and tossed.","year":60},{"id":"recdNRRMDDydaTXat","ref":"Jas.1.7","text":"For let not that man think that he shall receive any thing of the Lord.","year":60},{"id":"recG80F6tbc5FiIPz","ref":"Jas.1.8","text":"A double minded man is unstable in all his ways.","year":60}]}
